# Daily UI/UX Flow Optimization


## Document Overview


This document provides a comprehensive approach to optimizing the UI/UX flows of highly trafficked pages within the Forgotten Formula PMA's digital platform. The targeted files for this optimization are the `client/src/pages/landing.tsx` and `client/src/pages/member-dashboard.tsx`. The objective is to enhance aesthetics, interaction, and design to align with modern principles, thereby improving the user experience and supporting the mission of facilitating true healing.


